text: Ærest on corsan stream up on þone ealdan stan weall suð oðða hyrnan.
Of cildastane on merces burh norðwearde þonne west on þa burh oðða west hyrnan þanne norþ on herepað oð þone ænlipigan ðorn.
West þanne on þone hrycg<../images/tbar.gif>on þone ænlipian stan.
Þanne norþrihte on mere mæde westewearde þanne rihte on þone herepað oþ wifeles cumbes heafod.
Þonne of þære suð ecge on æscwylle oð<../images/tbar.gif>nehste slæd.
Þanne on stanwylles broc of dune on afene.
